comments: Davis (LAL) rests his hand on Nurkic's (POR) back as Nurkic starts his upward shooting motion and Davis cleanly blocks the shot attempt thereafter.
Bradley (LAL) legally contests Simons' (POR) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Winslow (POR) and James (LAL) engage and disengage with one another off-ball.
Winslow (POR) backs up toward Johnson (LAL) and marginal body contact occurs as Johnson pivots.
Smith Jr. (POR) is moving forward as he sets the pick on Bradley (LAL) and marginal contact occurs to Bradley's side as the defensive switch takes place.
Nurkic's (POR) arms come out slightly as he sets the pick on Horton-Tucker (LAL), and marginal contact occurs as Nurkic releases away to roll.
Horton-Tucker (LAL) brings his left arm out toward Simons' (POR) path and marginal contact occurs to Simons' front as he turns to drive.
James (LAL) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Winslow (POR) before incidental body contact occurs.
Johnson (LAL) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Horton-Tucker (LAL) lowers his left shoulder and delivers contact to Elleby's (POR) side, dislodging Elleby from his defensive position.
Monk (LAL) moves alongside Simons' (POR) path with a collapsed forearm when marginal contact occurs to Simons' front during his drive and after his gather.
Elleby (POR) brushes Horton-Tucker's (LAL) left arm and marginal contact occurs after Horton-Tucker secures the rebound.

Smith Jr. (POR) is retreating toward the baseline when marginal body contact occurs with James (LAL) during the driving shot attempt. Smith Jr. avoids making contact with James' left arm as he swipes down.
Nurkic (POR) makes clean contact with the ball and bats it toward himself as incidental arm contact occurs with Bradley (LAL).
James (LAL) swipes down and delivers contact into Nurkic's (POR) arm, affecting his SQBR in the backcourt.
Horton-Tucker (LAL) doesn't maintain a legal guarding position as he extends his arm into Smith Jr.'s (POR) path, making arm and body contact that affects his driving shot attempt.
Horton-Tucker's (LAL) left leg is extended outward when marginal contact occurs with Elleby (POR) as the long rebound ricochets away.
Monk (LAL) commits a take foul on Nurkic (POR).
Simons (POR) and Monk (LAL) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Monk (LAL) commits a take foul on Simons (POR).
McLemore (POR) legally contests James' (LAL) jump shot attempt.
